Package oopds.assignment.DC.services

Class NgoQueueService

java.lang.Object
oopds.assignment.DC.services.NgoQueueService
@Service public class NgoQueueService extends Object
A Service Class to be used by the Spring API to do certain operations based on the method called. This service class contains the operations that involves the NgoQueue.
